snippet.title: Nyanroo The Supercat Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
WE ARE LIVE ON KICKSTARTER

Support our campaign in the link below

https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1392070915/nyanroo-the-supercat
https://www.nyanroo.com

Nyanroo The Supercat is a platform game inspired by the 16-bit era, where you play as a cat hero trying to save the world from a gang of evil dogs!
